onauten.me/?page_id=19',0,'page','',0),(20,1,'2015-04-03 21:21:03','2015-04-03 21:21:03','','Nieuws','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-v1','','','2015-04-03 21:21:03','2015-04-03 21:21:03','',19,'http://wpastronauten.me/19-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(21,1,'2015-04-03 21:21:19','2015-04-03 21:21:19','motivatietekst\r\n<h1> Voorstellingen</h1>\r\n<h2>De verwendoos</h2>\r\nTroetelvoorstelling waarmee we op dit moment door Nederland touren\r\n\r\n[gallery size=\"large\" link=\"none\" columns=\"2\" ids=\"58,63,64,62\"]\r\n<h2>Verwenworkshop</h2>\r\nTest\r\n\r\n[gallery size=\"large\" link=\"none\" ids=\"62,58\"]\r\n<h2>De Astronauten</h2>\r\nEerste project van De Astronauten. Een samenkomst van beeldende kunst en theater. Wij hebben op verschillende festivals gestaan, zoals het bevrijdingsfestival te Wageningen, het BAM festival van Hengelo en The Indian Summer Festival in Broek op Langendijk.\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"none\" size=\"large\" columns=\"2\" ids=\"68,69,70,67\"]','Boek Ons','','publish','open','open','','huur-ons','','','2015-04-08 10:28:29','2015-04-08 10:28:29','',0,'http://wpastronauten.me/?page_id=21',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2015-04-03 21:21:19','2015-04-03 21:21:19','','Huur Ons','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-v1','','','2015-04-03 21:21:19','2015-04-03 21:21:19','',21,'http://wpastronauten.me/21-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(23,1,'2015-04-03 21:21:45','2015-04-03 21:21:45','[gallery columns=\"2\" link=\"none\" size=\"large\" ids=\"70,68,69,67,64,63,62,58\"]','Fotos en Videos','','publish','open','open','','media','','','2015-04-03 23:15:46','2015-04-03 23:15:46','',0,'http://wpastronauten.me/?page_id=23',0,'page','',0),(24,1,'2015-04-03 21:21:45','2015-04-03 21:21:45','','Fotos en Videos','','inherit','open','open','','23-revision-v1','','','2015-04-03 21:21:45','2015-04-03 21:21:45','',23,'http://wpastronauten.me/23-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(25,1,'2015-04-03 21:22:39','2015-04-03 21:22:39','[contact-form-7 id=\"49\" t